<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    
    <hr>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "picture.png", width: 300, alt: "profile image" %>
        
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            
          <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div 
                class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                role="progressbar"
                aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                aria-valuemax="100"
                style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
              >
                
              </div>
            </div>
          
          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>As a current  high school and early college student at NUAMES, I have been trying to get my associates degree. Although there are coding classes offered through  Weber I can take, I have to decided to take the Code to Success course in order to get ahead.</p>
      
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Arbys :|
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              :|
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              NUAMES
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Weber State University
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
